Lenny Von Dohlen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lenny_Von_Dohlen 0 Lenny Von Dohlen (born December 22, 1958) is an American film, television and stage actor, known for his performance as architect Miles Harding in the film Electric Dreams and as the orchid-growing agoraphobic Harold Smith in the television series Twin Peaks.
